{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f36be83694","title":"周恩来、康生、陈伯达、江青、关锋、戚本禹接见贵州省军区司令员何光宇、副政委李再含的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9b00c2520","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":25,"articleId":"f36be83694","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"关锋","id":"00506c3c84","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"李再含","id":"d778f94355","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"11a0612519","type":"title","text":"周恩来、康生、陈伯达、江青、关锋、戚本禹接见贵州省军区司令员何光宇、副政委李再含的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fefa01770","type":"paragraph","text":"时间：一九六七年一月二十五日晚七时三十分至九时四十分。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aef051e858","type":"paragraph","text":"地点：人民大会堂。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6fa4e0ce3f","type":"paragraph","text":"( 李再含传达时说:总理对贵州情况很关心 )","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee305a9c54","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含: ( 谈到文化大革命中三类人员外出比较严重时 )","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c797cf1cf6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理: 这还了得,他们是不是发钱?是在本省,是在外省?","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ad33f7047","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含:本省有,到北京也有。主要是搞翻案。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a5da28b405","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：劳改、劳教人员闹翻案,就没有得完了。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"368eef472a","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含: (谈到省、市委中及厅局长中由郭x x发起组织战斗团时)","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ed6cff44d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理: 这样好嘛!这个更暴露了。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"399567073b","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含：他们(即省、市委中顽固分子)本身在搞串连。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff14ac4c36","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：他们本身搞串连到可能。是否可以夺权以后宣布个命令:擅离职守,不假外出都要开除。是否开除严重了。请考虑。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97f1f853ba","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含：他们本身去搞串连。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebff9780a7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：所有科长以上人员都要留在工作岗位上。如果不假外出,要给予处分。他们搞串连是搞反串连。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"831951a55c","type":"paragraph","text":"李再含: (谈到李明远时)","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d2b5828340","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：曹狄秋就是指定工会主席组织上海赤卫队（注:上海赤卫队是保守派组织)。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"91954ef571","type":"paragraph","text":"何光宇: (谈到李铁乃问题时)李铁乃掌握几百辆车子。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"16c5af973c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：现在还是这样?","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7c54db487","type":"paragraph","text":"何光宇：现在不是了。李铁乃夺枪。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1bc66c4e61","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：夺枪是为了拿到所谓证据,不然他们就不会到北京来了。明天(元月二十六日)要宣布命令，出个布告公布说:奉中央指示逮捕红卫军头子,在北京捕了,在贵阳的也要捕,他们是反革命。但,群众是好的。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fdc54cd76e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：并宣布造反派夺省市委的权,军区支持。那就大快人心了。具体怎么办?按主席指示,你们要确定政策,如对中层以上干部要限制,不假外出要处分。一个是逮捕的命令；一个是军队支持的命令,今晚(元月二十五日)你们要研究好。明天再谈。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4ac1d4c4f","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：邓振新编著《贵州风云》(香港：中国国际文艺出版社，2014)。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f36be83694","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}